# Database Seeds

This folder contains SQL files that populate your local development database with test data.

## Files

- **01-users.sql** - Test user accounts (password: `Test1234!`)
- **02-profiles.sql** - User profile data (update based on your schema)
- **03-example-data.sql** - Your application-specific data (customize)

